# Blog Website Design

This project is a simple blog website design with a header, sidebar, content area, and footer. It is built using HTML and CSS, and it provides a basic structure that you can expand upon for your blog content.

## Introduction

This project is a static blog website design with a responsive layout. It consists of a header, sidebar, content area, and footer. The goal is to provide a starting point for a blog website that you can customize according to your content and styling preferences.

## Project Structure

- **`index.html`:** Main HTML file containing the structure of the website.
- **`style.css`:** CSS file for styling the HTML elements.

## Preview

Include screenshots or GIFs of your blog website to give users a quick preview.

